            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Ex auctoritate <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan> Caesaris divi <lb n="3"/>Traiani Parthici <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilii</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>divi Nervae nepotis <lb n="5"/>Traiani Hadriani <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pontif</abbr><ex>icis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>potest</abbr><ex>ate</ex></expan> V <expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan> IIII co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulis</ex></expan> III <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Messius Rusticus curator <lb n="9"/>alvei et riparum Tiberis et <lb n="10"/>cloacarum urbis <expan><abbr>r</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>r</abbr><ex>igore</ex></expan> restituit <lb n="11"/>secundum praecedentem <lb n="12"/>terminationem <expan><abbr>proxim</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>cipp</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <lb n="13"/><expan><abbr>ped</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> XXIX <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>emis</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: zwischen dem 10. Dezember 120 n. Chr. und dem 9. Dezember 121 n. Chr. Terminalcippus.</p>
            </div>
